name: EWebkit
body:
### EWebKit
As a part of [enlightenment](https://www.enlightenment.org/) framework, EWebKit has supported WebView widget. Besides EWebKit has been used for [Tizen](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tizen) platform. All Tizen products are using EWebKit to support web browser and web applications.

### Build
1. $ ./Tools/efl/install-dependencies 
2. $ ./Tools/Scripts/build-webkit --efl [--update-efl]

### Run
* $ ./Tools/Scripts/run-minibrowser --efl

### Contributors
Many developers have been contributing to EWebKit project since 2010. You can find EWebKit contributors in [WebKit Team](https://webkit.org/team/)

### Support
* [EFLWebKit Wiki](https://trac.webkit.org/wiki/EFLWebKit)
* [EFLWebKit buildbot status](https://build.webkit.org/console?category=EFL)

 * [webkit-dev](https://lists.webkit.org/mailman/listinfo/webkit-dev)
* #webkit-efl on freenode
